@Space Lion
The alien invasion only happens twice in that universe and they're more concerned in capturing women for whatever they want them for.

Pokemon is an even more dangerous place to live because Raticates can tear houses in minutes, getting burned by a Houndoom hurts forever, Tyranitar can change entire landscapes when it rages, Muk is so poisonous that even his footprints can kill, Duskull and Drfiloon steal children, etc. At least with Duke Nukem around, it's can guaranteed any threat (and political asshats) will get their asses kicked.
